tive service demand with qualified technicians.', '$12B-$18B', 'high', 'critical', 'Vehicle owners aged 25-65 seeking convenient, same-day automotive repair services in urban and suburban areas', 8, '["Commission-based marketplace connecting customers with independent mobile mechanics (15-25% per transaction)", "Subscription model offering priority booking and diagnostic services with included mobile mechanic visits", "B2B fleet maintenance contracts for corporate vehicle management with guaranteed response times"]', NULL, '["High competition from established platforms (TaskRabbit, Angie''s List, manufacturer service networks)", "Quality control and liability challenges with third-party mechanics performing work in customer locations", "Regulatory compliance and licensing verification requirements varying by jurisdiction", "High customer acquisition costs in competitive automotive services market"]', '["Conduct market research surveying 100+ vehicle owners about pain points with current repair options and willingness to pay premium for mobile services", "Analyze competitor landscape (existing mobile mechanic platforms, traditional shops offering mobile services) to identify differentiation opportunities", "Interview 20+ independent mobile mechanics about platform needs, commission tolerance, and current customer acquisition challenges"]', NULL, 'Consumers need immediate, reliable automotive repair services without traveling to physical locations, while the current market suffers from trust and quality assurance issues as evidenced by widespread scam reports.', NULL, 37.9864, -122.135, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
